Featured Location – Nevada Ranches
Elko Land and Livestock Company (ELLCo), a subsidiary of Newmont, owns and operates several ranches in Nevada.
Learn More








Featured Location – Yanacocha
Yanacocha operates with integrity, trust and respect to create not only profitable production but also generate sustainable development and opportunity in the region.
Learn More










