      currency fluctuations, increased production costs, variances in ore
      grade or recovery rates from those assumed in mining plans and other
      operational risks, geotechnical, metallurgical and hydrological risks,
      political and community relations risk, and changes in governmental
      regulation and requirements. For a discussion of such risks relating to
      our business and other factors, see the Company’s Form 10-K, filed on or
      about February 21, 2017, with the Securities and Exchange Commission
